data.title: 2013) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Richard D. Carter, age 76, of Bemidji, MN, died Friday, May 3, 2013 at his home.   Funeral Services will be 2:00 P.M. Tuesday, May 7, 2013 at Bethel Lutheran Church, Bemidji, MN with Rev. Mark Kindem officiating. Visitation will be from 5 PM to 7 PM Monday evening at the Olson-Schwartz Funeral Home and for one hour...
